```

**Frontend Build:**
```bash
VITE_API_URL=https://yourdomain.hosting.com/api npm run build
# Output: dist/ with API URL hardcoded to Hosting.com
```

**Upload:**
```
Backend: Hosting.com (Passenger + Node.js)
Frontend: public_html/ecoms/
```

**Result:**
- Frontend: `https://yourdomain.hosting.com/ecoms/`
- API: `https://yourdomain.hosting.com/api`

